[38.875, "o", "\r\n"]
[38.875, "o", "\u001b[1;36m\u2501\u2501\u2501 Step 4: The fix \u2014 ACS collector sidecar inside the Kata VM \u2501\u2501\u2501\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[41.375, "o", "\r\n"]
[41.375, "o", "A second ACS collector runs as a privileged sidecar inside\r\n"]
[41.425, "o", "the Kata pod. It attaches core_bpf probes to the guest kernel\r\n"]
[41.475, "o", "and sends events to the ACS sensor on the host.\r\n"]
